# Template Smoke Test

```powershell
$TEMP_DIR = Join-Path $env:TEMP ("sumitapp-" + [guid]::NewGuid())
mkdir $TEMP_DIR | Out-Null
npx create-sumit-app $TEMP_DIR

bun --cwd $TEMP_DIR dev
bun --cwd $TEMP_DIR build
bun --cwd $TEMP_DIR lint
bun --cwd $TEMP_DIR check-types

# Cleanup when done (optional)
# Remove-Item -Recurse -Force $TEMP_DIR
```
